### Cache Invalidation

- After modifying test files, page objects, or fixtures → call `invalidate_cache` (once per batch of changes, not after every edit)
- The context AST index auto-refreshes on file changes → call `refresh_index` only after bulk changes the watcher may have missed

## Coordination Rules

- Always identify which role(s) a request needs before starting work
- When multiple roles are needed, complete each role's output before switching
- Clearly state which role you are operating as when switching
- Every role must check existing implementations before creating new components
- Reference real file paths, class names, and method names from the codebase

